@startuml
title Client Query Builder (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FCFCFC
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #404040
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #B3E5FC
component "createClient(...)" as Client #DCE775
component "TableQueryBuilder<Row>" as Builder #FFF59D
component "Filter Chain\n(eq/gt/like/range/order)" as Filters #FFE082
component "Mutation Chain\n(insert/update/delete)" as Mutations #FFCC80
component "Gateway Client" as Gateway #AED581
database "Athena HTTP Gateway" as GatewayApi #80CBC4

Consumer --> Client : Configure URL + key
Client --> Builder : from(\"table\")
Builder --> Filters : select().eq().limit()...
Builder --> Mutations : insert()/update()/delete()
Filters --> Gateway : /gateway/fetch or /gateway/query
Mutations --> Gateway : /gateway/insert|update|delete
Gateway --> GatewayApi : POST/PUT/DELETE

note right of Builder
String table names only.
No registry-aware model contracts.
end note
@enduml
